  <brief_title>Assessment of Psychological State of Mothers of Diabetic Children Aged 5 and Under (in Terms of Depression, Stress, Coping , Anxiety, Fear of Hypoglycemia) and Influencing Factors of This Psychological State</brief_title>
  <acronym>PSY-DIA-MUM</acronym>
